Cameron is a South African born Senior Software Developer
working in Berlin. He is a meticulous, driven and hard-working
individual with a passion for all things Tech. In his free time he
enjoys attending developer meetups, going for bike rides and
playing football. He is currently learning to speak German and
aspires to become fluent, in both speaking and writing.
When Cameron finds himself wanting to make a spontaneous
purchase, whether in-store or online, his immediate thoughts are
whether or not he can afford to. Due to numerous debit orders
being paid at different times of the month, his current banking
app does not accurately reflect what his net balance will be after
all orders have been paid. This is where Finanzer steps in.
